# Systemd Service 示例

## 1. 每小时健康巡检

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-health-check.service
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Platform Health Check
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=/bin/bash /home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_hourly_health_check.sh
WorkingDirectory=/home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace
User=sandbox
Group=sandbox

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-health-check.timer
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Run platform health check hourly

[Timer]
OnCalendar=hourly
Persistent=true

[Install]
WantedBy=timers.target
```

## 2. 每日备份

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-daily-backup.service
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Platform Daily Backup
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=/bin/bash /home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_daily_backup.sh
WorkingDirectory=/home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace
User=sandbox
Group=sandbox

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-daily-backup.timer
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Run platform daily backup at 3 AM

[Timer]
OnCalendar=*-*-* 03:00:00
Persistent=true

[Install]
WantedBy=timers.target
```

## 3. 每周清理

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-weekly-cleanup.service
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Platform Weekly Cleanup
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=/bin/bash /home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_weekly_cleanup.sh
WorkingDirectory=/home/sandbox/.openclaw/workspace
User=sandbox
Group=sandbox

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

### /etc/systemd/system/platform-weekly-cleanup.timer
```ini
[Unit]
Description=Run platform weekly cleanup on Sunday at 4 AM

[Timer]
OnCalendar=Sun *-*-* 04:00:00
Persistent=true

[Install]
WantedBy=timers.target
```

## 启用方法

```bash
# 启用健康巡检
sudo systemctl enable platform-health-check.timer
sudo systemctl start platform-health-check.timer

# 启用每日备份
sudo systemctl enable platform-daily-backup.timer
sudo systemctl start platform-daily-backup.timer

# 启用每周清理
sudo systemctl enable platform-weekly-cleanup.timer
sudo systemctl start platform-weekly-cleanup.timer

# 查看状态
systemctl list-timers
```
